DESCRIPTION:
- You can view your collection of cards if you use the command 'sc'. The collections can be sorted by Name, Gen, Wishlist, Cosmetics Applied, Card stats,  3d Availability and can also be filtered by wishlist or gen number or tag name.
-Type sc t:ut to find untagged cards from your collection
SLASH_DESC: Enter the user you want to see the collection of
SLASH_DESC2: Enter the filter you want to apply to the collection
PLAYER_PRIVATE: {{author}} | Collection of that user is private!
NO_CARDS_FOUND: {{author}} | No cards matching your search were found
NO_TAG_FOUND: Appreciate the tagging effort but no tags found
